Elyse
Hi Every one i have started a relay for life team and i could use your help! I need to raise money to help crush all the other teams in the relay. The money goes to the American Cancer Society to help find a cure for cancer. The event is April 17 and if you want to i'm always excepting new members. All you have to do is go to my facebook page and click on support me, or join. to make a donations or become a member. Every little bit is apreciated. 

Thanks 
        Elyse
